title: Jerry Seinfeld is world's highest paid comedian
text: Jerry Seinfeld is world's highest paid comedian Thursday, 22 October 2015 (9 minutes ago) Jerry Seinfeld has been named as the world's highest paid comedian by Forbes. Jerry Seinfeld Is the Most Highest-Paid Comedian According to Forbes Forbes 00:39 Jerry Seinfeld still reigns supreme in the land of funny people, at least in terms of financial earnings for the year.
